  "title": "Buying the Necessary Groceries",
  "lessonText": "Understanding what ingredients to purchase is crucial for making a delicious chicken curry.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Identify key ingredients: chicken, spices, vegetables.\n- Choose fresh produce: onions, garlic, tomatoes.\n- Select quality chicken: consider organic or free-range.\n- Gather spices: curry powder, cumin, coriander.\n- Don't forget essentials: cooking oil, salt, and pepper."
  }
}
